  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t1911年10月10日武昌起义，广州人打响第一枪！<br/>\r\n两个月后满清皇帝退位，历时276年满清统治以及2200年君主專制覆灭。<br/>\r\n1912年中华民国临时政府诞生，孙中山就任临时总统。<br/>\r\n不过孙中山这个人我不了解，只知道他和鲁迅一样早期从医，后来发现学医救不了中国人于是弃医从文从政。<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZTk1M2NlMjNhNGYzMjZkNjZlMWUzLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMjgwJmhlaWdodD0xODQw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e953ce23a4f326d66e1e3.jpg?width=1280&amp;height=1840\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e953ce23a4f326d66e1e3.jpg?width=1280&amp;height=1840\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e953ce23a4f326d66e1e3.jpg?width=1280&amp;height=1840\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZDBlNTI5NDUxNmY4N2JmZDFmMjYxLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMjgwJmhlaWdodD0xNDI4\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d0e5294516f87bfd1f261.jpg?width=1280&amp;height=1428\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d0e5294516f87bfd1f261.jpg?width=1280&amp;height=1428\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d0e5294516f87bfd1f261.jpg?width=1280&amp;height=1428\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZmRlZGI1M2E5NmIzNmJjODM5N2ZlLnBuZz93aWR0aD0xMDI0JmhlaWdodD02NDA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fdedb53a96b36bc8397fe.png?width=1024&amp;height=640\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fdedb53a96b36bc8397fe.png?width=1024&amp;height=640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fdedb53a96b36bc8397fe.png?width=1024&amp;height=640\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
